{"tid":2451010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登批普京干預美國大選 俄羅斯召回駐美大使","createTime":"2021-03-17T21:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T23:10:09.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1c39676498e4dfbb2f6e291c059ce2caefab1542","tid":2451010,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:13:55.000Z","msg":"（中央社莫斯科17日綜合外電報導）美國總統拜登稱俄羅斯總統蒲亭將為干預美國大選「付出代價」後，俄國政府今天將駐美國大使召回莫斯科，以商議俄美未來關係。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n俄國則稱相關指控毫無根據。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯外交部透過聲明表示，已將駐美大使安托諾夫（Anatoly Antonov）召回莫斯科，以討論俄美關係的未來。<br />\n<br />\n聲明並指出，這項行動目的在於確保雙邊關係不會無可挽回地惡化。<br />\n<br />\n拜登17日接受「美國廣播公司新聞網」（ABC News ）訪問時還說，他同意蒲亭是個「劊子手」，對政敵冷酷無情。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n（譯者：楊昭彥）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202103180006.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202103180006.aspx&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2XpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=889de23b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202103180006.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"84a904a083847f5e7715199a7321d0a8e982e6a7","tid":2451010,"uid":66324,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:16:52.000Z","msg":"萬能稻草人: 俄佬"},{"pid":"6a4676b77c69379e5013c017eb392839b62de92b","tid":2451010,"uid":157411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:18:37.000Z","msg":"拜登會唔會UP鳩錯蘇聯總統 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbf790342682aa8149ff2f746004e957d9238c0","tid":2451010,"uid":331949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:22:01.000Z","msg":"Russia is just a scapegoat!"},{"pid":"eec4e32101b33b2b5dc4f7c87d0be11b4d160543","tid":2451010,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:23:20.000Z","msg":"Talk and distracting action<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9ebdb59743b97c42687544678c7fd76d9de1d1","tid":2451010,"uid":2568